ActDepartment of Health Act
SubjectCanadian Thalidomide Survivors Support Program Order
PrecisOrder Establishing the CANADIAN THALIDOMIDE SURVIVORS SUPPORT PROGRAM in order to set out the parameters for a federal financial support program for victims of thalidomide, called the CANADIAN THALIDOMIDE SURVIVORS SUPPORT PROGRAM, which would replace the current Thalidomide Survivors Contribution Program.
